I'm trying to figure out why I can't write to the overlay when it seems to be mounted by the world-agent service as root, which typically allows setting xattrs. If that's the case, overlay operations should work, right? I checked the writable directory with `touch /project/writable/test`, but I got an EPERM error. Maybe overlayfs is acting as read-only despite having rw flags. It's puzzling since we can write directly to the upper directory. I'm left wondering if something in the mount configuration is blocking write operations.
